-- American Express selectively cutting credit lines: CEO
-- 
-- Mon Jul 21, 2008 5:27pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/21/us-americanexpress-ceo-idUSGOR17695420080721

 

 (Reuters) - American Express Co ( AXP.N ) is selectively cutting back credit lines for U.S. customers, CEO Kenneth Cheanult said on Monday.  

 The credit card issuer and processing network is also scaling back efforts to gain new U.S. customers, while expanding internationally and in business to business card products